<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin.ApiFamily" Title="ApiFamily enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin">IRendererPlugin</PageRef> ->
    ApiFamily
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ApiFamily</TypeRef> enumeration identifies the graphics API family implemented by a renderer plugin.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="OpenGL">
        Specifies an OpenGL renderer.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="OpenGLES">
        Specifies an OpenGL ES renderer.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Direct3D">
        Specifies a Microsoft Direct3D renderer. Direct3D renderers are available on Windows.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Vulkan">
        Specifies a Vulkan renderer.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Metal">
        Specifies a Metal renderer. Metal renderers are available on macOS.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator.FilterPluginsOfFamily">RenderPluginEnumerator.FilterPluginsOfFamily</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
